This is a patch for SLPVectorizer:

[SLP]Improve minbitwidth analysis for abs/smin/smax/umin/umax intrinsics.
[SLP]Improve minbitwidth analysis for abs/smin/smax/umin/umax intrinsics.

https://alive2.llvm.org/ce/z/ivPZ26 for the abs transformations.

